Package nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.util.functional

@NonNullByDefault package nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.util.functional
This package contains classes related to functional programming, such as versions of Function, Supplier, and BiFunction that throw checked exceptions.

Other classes in this package are versions of functional interfaces with different types or counts of parameters compared to existing interfaces. For example the TriIntConsumer.
